title: Full Disclosure on “My Unorthodox Life” ft. Batsheva Haart
description:
Netflix is in the house!!
My Unorthodox Life star, Batsheva Haart gets real about her transition from living in an ultra-orthodox community to making the move to New York City. Lauren & Jeremy gain an entirely new perspective on religion, fashion, love, and family in one of the most inspiring episodes to date.
